eu.geclipse.core
Class Extensions

java.lang.Object
  eu.geclipse.core.Extensions

public class Extensions
extends java.lang.Object

This is a helper class that holds static fields and methods to easily access extension of the g-Eclipse core extension points.

getRegisteredAuthTokenNames

public static java.util.List<java.lang.String> getRegisteredAuthTokenNames()
Get a list with the names of all registered authentication tokens. The list will be sorted alphabetically.

Returns:
A list containing the names of the types of all currently available tokens.

getRegisteredAuthTokenDescriptions

public static java.util.List<IAuthenticationTokenDescription> getRegisteredAuthTokenDescriptions()
Get a list of all currently registered authentication token description.

Returns:
A list containing instances of all currently registered extensions of the authentication token description configuration elements.

getRegisteredFilesystemSchemes

public static java.util.List<java.lang.String> getRegisteredFilesystemSchemes()
Get a list of all currently registered filesystem schemes.

Returns:
A list of Strings containing all schemes that are currently known by the EFS.
